snippet.title: Garbage Pail Kids: Mad Mike and the Quest for Stale Gum - Gameplay Launch Trailer | PS4 Games
snippet.description:
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10004504

The Garbage Pail Kids are back in this Long-Lost, All-New platforming adventure. Featuring four playable characters, six secret-filled levels, and a trading-card system, Garbage Pail Kids: Mad Mike and the Quest for Stale Gum is a throwback to the golden era of 80's gaming. Available NOW for PlayStation 4. 

#ps4games #ps4
